::The Galactors::

The two Galactor jets turn, heading away from the Brotherhood base. 
The attack had failed, but it was never designed to succeed. It did 
what it was meant to do, and that was to divert the attentions of 
Hell Beast's troops from the battle at the Cybertronian Fire. That 
battle was over, anyways.

Powering up their afterburners, the two jets blast off toward 
Alliance island.
